rows.label: qev040902_MSG0001
rows.name:
Brotherpon will come home holding aloft blindingly
shiny Sword of Legendaryness![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040902_MSG0002
rows.name: Moimoi can see it now![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040902_MSG0003
rows.name:
Though, hmm... If sword is truly blinding,
Moimoi may not see much after that.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040902_MSG0004
rows.name: So tasty! So happy![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040902_MSG0005
rows.name: Wh-what is going on? Why has party already started?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040902_MSG0006
rows.name: Ah! Muimui! Brotherpon![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040902_MSG0007
rows.name:
Moimoi was so hungry that he start in on food
tiiiiiny bit early.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040902_MSG0008
rows.name:
But Muimui just collected heaping mountain of cash,
so we can keep ordering more![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040902_JNK0010
rows.name: Lecture

rows.label: qev040902_SEL0011
rows.name: Lay into Moimoi for starting without you.

rows.label: qev040902_JNK0020
rows.name: Turn the Tables

rows.label: qev040902_SEL0021
rows.name:
Tell Muimui that this can be
his way of repaying Moimoi.

rows.label: qev040902_MSG0009
rows.name: S-sorry... But Moimoi not eaten a real meal in weeks.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040902_MSG0010
rows.name:
Having all this food lined up in front of eyes...
Moimoi could not resist![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040902_MSG0011
rows.name:
Muimui can certainly relate to how hard it is to go
hungry.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040902_MSG0012
rows.name:
True... Muimui never could have come so far without
help of brotherpon.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040902_MSG0013
rows.name:
And all this questing could not have been easy on
poor Moimoi.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040902_MSG0014
rows.name: Friend is right! Moimoi not need to apologize![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040902_MSG0015
rows.name:
Plus, now that Muimui is fabulously wealthy,
little things do not matter anymore.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040902_MSG0016
rows.name:
Heh heh! Muimui go order more food!
Friend and brotherpon wait here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040902_MSG0017
rows.name:
Tab is on Muimui today, [ST:playername ]!
Eat until food spills out of ears of friend![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040902_MSG0018
rows.name: Wooo! Brotherpon coolest Nopon ever![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040902_MSG0019
rows.name: ...Grk! GYAAAAAAAAUGH![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040902_MSG0020
rows.name: SO EXPENSIVE![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040902_MSG0021
rows.name: The...the bill is...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040902_MSG0022
rows.name:
It is same amount as Muimui earned as reward!
HOW MUCH DID MOIMOI EAT?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040902_MSG0023
rows.name:
Er, Moimoi black out halfway through from sheer joy.
Memory foggy after course 17.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040902_MSG0024
rows.name:
This mean we are poor again!
And Muimui STILL hungry![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040902_JNK0030
rows.name: Lecture

rows.label: qev040902_SEL0031
rows.name: Chastise Moimoi for overeating.

rows.label: qev040902_JNK0040
rows.name: Console

rows.label: qev040902_SEL0041
rows.name: Tell Muimui that he will just have to start over again.

rows.label: qev040902_MSG0025
rows.name: B-but... Moimoi not had food in sooo looooong...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040902_MSG0026
rows.name: Because brotherpon refuse to ever work![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040902_MSG0027
rows.name:
Gah! Muimui not let brotherpon turn this around!
Give it back! All of it! Every bite![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040902_MSG0028
rows.name:
What? No! Being BLADE way too scary!
Muimui not do more of that for long time.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040902_MSG0029
rows.name: So Moimoi has to give it back! All of it! Every bite![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040902_MSG0030
rows.name:
Moimoi is genius inventioner, but that simply not
possible.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040902_MSG0031
rows.name:
More realistic for Muimui to stop making
impossible demands and just get job.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040902_MSG0032
rows.name: Rraaagh! Moimoi teach brotherpon to take that tone![ST:wait ]
